text: Walter Reyno (13 February 1935 - 3 December 2014) was a Uruguayan actor and theater director. He was known for his roles in 25 Watts, El ojo en la nuca, and in El aura. Reyno was born in Montevideo, Uruguay. Reyno died from respiratory failure in Montevideo, Uruguay, aged 79. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1935 births Category:2014 deaths Category:Actors from Montevideo Category:Theater
